comments: Great prof, not only knows the subject matters but she lives to teach. Lectures are interesting, informative and funny. She tests you on exactly what she says she will test you on. Also the best looking teacher I have ever had. Wish I could take in other subjects. Favorite all-time prof.

AWESOME TEACHER! She\'s very engaging. Provides study guides for test that contain EXACTLY what she tests you on. Provides worksheets to help remember concepts. I really enjoyed her class! She gives you every opportunity to get an A. I wish she was teaching Bio 241 so I could take her again.
